1
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:09,800
So I

2
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,160
killed her.

3
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,160
You killed her?

4
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,280
Didn't she die of illness?

5
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,960
It was also the third day of the ninth month.

6
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:19,000
I drank a lot of wine.

7
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,760
I came home very late.

8
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,520
Master.

9
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:24,120
Careful.

10
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:24,840
Slow down.

11
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:26,760
Slow down.

12
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:27,680
Watch your step.

13
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,120
Master.

14
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,240
It's First Wife.

15
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,360
Today is my husband's birthday.

16
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,640
This one came here specially

17
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:51,160
to sing The Drunken Concubine for my husband.

18
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,560
Consider it a gift

19
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,440
to celebrate my husband's birthday.

20
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:56,640
Good.

21
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,280
I am happy today.

22
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,360
It's been a long time since I heard you

23
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,440
sing for me.

24
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,160
What's wrong with you?

25
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,200
Lai Fu!

26
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,600
Lai Fu!

27
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:52,200
Call a doctor!

28
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,440
Go call a doctor!

29
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,960
I'll go right away!

30
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,040
Madam!

31
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,120
Madam, why?

32
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:02,160
You don't love me anymore.

33
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,600
You don't love me.

34
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:08,880
Living...

35
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,400
what's the point?

36
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,040
I...

37
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,320
I will never...

38
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,760
never...

39
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,440
forgive you.

40
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,960
So to speak,

41
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,800
you neglected Bai Mei,

42
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,480
which led to her suicide.

43
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:47,960
It was me.

44
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:49,640
It was us.

45
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:52,920
Us?

46
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:53,920
Me,

47
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:55,800
my mother,

48
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,120
Zi Feng,

49
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,160
everyone in the Lin Family.

50
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,280
We were all pushing her.

51
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,320
Pushing her?

52
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,320
Why did you push her?

53
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,800
Just because of something she said in her sleep?

54
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,720
It wasn't just sleep talk.

55
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,520
I saw with my own eyes

56
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,400
her secret rendezvous with that man.

57
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:12,520
Master,

58
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:13,760
look.

59
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,920
Isn't that Madam Bai and Eldest Senior Brother?

60
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,040
In broad daylight,

61
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,160
have they no shame?

62
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,160
Master!

63
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,320
Who is he?

64
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,240
Zi Feng said

65
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,080
that was their Eldest Senior Brother.

66
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,560
Although I don't know his name,

67
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,880
I am certain

68
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:42,120
he must be the Brother Ying she mentioned in her sleep.

69
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,480
Why are you so certain?

70
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,400
Because Zi Feng and Bai Mei

71
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:49,440
had known each other at the theater for years.

72
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,840
She had seen many times

73
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,880
their secret rendezvous.

74
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,040
Go find her.

75
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,840
But no matter how much you blame yourself,

76
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,280
you didn't kill her.

77
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,200
I don't understand why

78
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,760
you went to such great lengths

79
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,480
to hide the truth

80
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:03,640
and say Bai Mei died of illness.

81
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,640
This is the Lin Family's internal rule.

82
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,800
I didn't want outsiders to know.

83
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,320
But by not telling,

84
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,840
you only invite more trouble.

85
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,800
The Lin Family's ancestral teachings state

86
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,480
that those who commit suicide

87
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,720
cannot enter the ancestral graves and Ancestral hall.

88
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:24,440
If the family elders

89
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,640
knew her true cause of death,

90
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,120
they wouldn't let her Ancestral tablet enter the Ancestral hall.

91
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,080
When she was alive,

92
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,680
I didn't cherish her properly.

93
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,200
So after she died,

94
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,840
I didn't want her soul

95
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,080
to have nowhere to return.

96
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,720
So I hid her true cause of death.

97
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:43,800
Inspector Huang,

98
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,840
what I told you today,

99
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,000
I hope you won't let outsiders know.

100
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,000
Rest assured, Master Lin.

101
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:07,600
What?

102
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:08,640
You're saying

103
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,200
Madam Bai committed suicide?

104
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,520
How pitiful.

105
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,440
Could it be

106
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,080
that the man

107
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,120
came back to avenge Bai Mei?

108
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,040
Unlikely.

109
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,760
The Lin Family case

110
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,240
was clearly done by an acquaintance.

111
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:24,920
If it were that man,

112
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,320
how would he know

113
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,640
the habits of everyone in the Lin Family?

114
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,040
Besides,

115
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,560
if Bai Mei really loved someone else,

116
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,280
she could have just eloped with him.

117
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,200
Why choose suicide?

118
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,480
And wearing

119
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,800
the costume from when she first met Master Lin,

120
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,440
singing the same opera,

121
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,160
and dying in his arms?

122
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,760
The only explanation

123
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:54,760
is that

124
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,400
when Madam Bai died,

125
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,760
she held a grudge.

126
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,240
To get her revenge,

127
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,440
she attached her vengeful ghost

128
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,840
to that costume,

129
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,920
and killed Old Mrs. Lin

130
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:05,960
and those two maids.

131
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,640
What is all this supernatural nonsense?

132
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,040
What do you mean?

133
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,920
I am the Guigu School's

134
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,480
72nd-generation direct disciple.

135
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:18,160
You dare question me?

136
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,960
Haven't you been investigating

137
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:22,080
and found absolutely nothing?

138
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,760
It seems for this case,

139
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,920
we can only start from the beginning.

140
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,040
Bai Mei.

141
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:04,200
Before going on stage that day,

142
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,040
if I hadn't sprained my ankle...

143
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,000
Miss,

144
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,000
please forgive my intrusion.

145
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,160
May I ask your name?

146
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:13,760
Quanzhou.

147
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,320
Bai Mei.

148
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:16,640
Bai Mei.

149
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,080
Good.

150
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,760
All of this was supposed to be mine,

151
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:32,120
but you stole it, you witch!

152
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,240
You witch!

153
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:35,720
Witch!

154
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:36,840
Witch!

155
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:40,760
But why?

156
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,800
You're already dead,

157
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,720
yet the Master still can't forget you.

158
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,200
And I

159
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:54,080
will always be beneath you.

160
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,200
But look!

161
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,440
Now, doesn't all of this

162
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,800
belong to me?

163
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,360
I am the Lin Family's

164
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,360
only mistress!

165
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:35,320
Zi Feng.

166
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,920
Why did you

167
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,960
frame me for adultery?

168
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,360
Why did you steal the Master from me?

169
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:43,960
Yes!

170
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:45,760
I framed you!

171
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,200
But so what?

172
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,680
You witch!

173
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:50,400
You're already dead,

174
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,880
yet you're a lingering ghost haunting the Master!

175
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,600
Haunting everyone in the Lin Family!

176
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,880
You are simply a venomous woman!

177
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:57,960
Give my Master back to me!

178
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,680
Give him back!

179
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:02,560
Venomous woman!

180
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,240
Go to hell!
